<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="联合类型数组" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#联合类型数组"><span>联合类型数组</span></a></h3>
